comment: Whiteside (MIA) firms up as he sets the screen on Caldwell-Pope (DET) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

Wade (MIA) leads with an unnatural extended leg into the mid-section of Drummond (DET). This contact trumps any contact by Drummond that affects the shot attempt and an offensive foul should be called.
R-SLASH shows that Whiteside (MIA) jumps from point A to point B and makes body contact with Morris (DET) that affects his driving layup attempt.
Udrih (MIA) hand checks Jackson (DET) and affects his RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Drummond (DET) sets the screen on Udrih (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
RHH shows that Jackson (DET) ends his dribble on his left foot and takes two legal steps prior to releasing his pass.
Tolliver (DET) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Bosh's (MIA) drive to the basket and step back shot attempt.
Udrih (MIA) allows Jackson (DET) to land after he attempts the jump shot. Any contact following the landing is incidental.
Bosh (MIA) sets the screen on Caldwell-Pope (DET) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bosh (MIA) commits a take foul on Drummond (DET).
Whiteside (MIA) reaches over Morris (DET) to grab the rebound but does not make any illegal contact or dislodge him.
Wade (MIA) and Caldwell-Pope (DET) briefly engage and separate away from the ball. Caldwell-Pope stumbles as he attempts to contest Bosh's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
